# Glossary in tab-separated format -*- coding: utf-8 -*-
yes	iihia
you're welcome	iihia
okay	iihia	masculine or neutral
affirmative iihia
yes	naaka	(women only), Feminine
Yes, it is correct	iihia, eelaamweekaneewiki
Miami	Myaamia	Myaamia, Irenwee
Language codes ISO	ISO 639-3	mia	ISO 639-3	mia
ILDA	Welcome to the Myaamia-Peewaalia dictionary	https://mc.miamioh.edu/ilda-myaamia/dictionary
no	moohci	moohci (part) No, not
moohci aweeya | Nobody
moohci, niiši neehi | No, I cannot
moohci iilwiaani | I said no
moohci noonki | Not now
moohci | No, not
not	moohci
welcome	meentitohkaalilaanki	we (excl.) welcome you (pl)
you're welcome	iihia
